    "en": {
      "title": "Marine cards worth Rs 50 lakh",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Forest officials yesterday recovered 480 kg of sea cards worth Rs 50 lakh stored near the Tamil Nadu-Mandapam for smuggling to Sri Lanka.",
        "Forest Department officials have received confidential information that sea cards are being stored near Mandapam from Vedalai beach area to be smuggled to Sri Lanka.",
        "After that, the forest department rushed to the area and confiscated the sea card weighing about 480 kg and is conducting an investigation.",
        "The forest department officials have said that the international value of the confiscated sea card will be 50 lakh rupees. (R)"
      ],
